<section id="To_remove_a_retirement_date_for_a_Virtual_Machine1" remap="TID_14862">
	<title>Removing a Retirement Date for a Virtual Machine</title>
	<para> 
		<productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> enables you to remove a retirement date for virtual machines.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Remove a Retirement Date for a Virtual Machine</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				From <menuchoice><guimenu>Infrastructure</guimenu><guisubmenu>Virtual Machines</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, click on the virtual machine that you want to remove the retirement date from.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2007.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> (<guilabel>Lifecycle</guilabel>), 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2008.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> (<guilabel>Set Retirement Dates</guilabel>).
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2009.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> (<guilabel>Remove retirement date</guilabel>).
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>